description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;We are looking for an enthusiastic, motivated and reliable Pharmacy Technician to fulfil the position of Deputy Dispensary Manager. This is a new position to help support our forward thinking dispensary and the implementation of 7 day services.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;North Devon District Hospital Pharmacy department has a fully automated dispensary serving all pharmaceutical needs of our integrated acute and community Trust. We also provide services to the local Mental Health Trust and Hospices, as well as our Outpatient clinics.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;You will work closely with the Dispensary Manager and the Medicines Optimisation team to ensure reduced numbers of omitted doses and timely discharges to ensure seamless patient flow, prioritising patient centred care at all times.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The South West has an excellent Dispensary Manger network to ensure consistency across the region, in the absence of the Dispensary Manager the successful candidate will be required to engage with the group.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;For further information please contact Dispensary Manager, Maria Phillips, mariaphillips1@nhs.net 01271 322395.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Closing Date 10/11/2020.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
